(1518, '_transient_su/generator/settings/scheduler', '<div id="su-generator-breadcrumbs"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="su-generator-home" title="Retourner à la liste des shortcodes">Tout les shortcodes</a> &rarr; <span>Scheduler</span> <small class="alignright">Allows to show the content only at the specified time period</small><div class="su-generator-clear"></div></div><div class="su-generator-note"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i><div class="su-generator-note-content"><p>This shortcode allows you to show content only at the specified time.</p>\n<p>Please pay special attention to the descriptions, which are located below each text field. It will save you a lot of time</p>\n<p>By default, the content of this shortcode will be visible all the time. By using fields below, you can add some limitations. For example, if you type 1-5 in the Days of the week field, content will be only shown from Monday to Friday. Using the same principles, you can limit content visibility from years to seconds.</p>\n</div></div><div class="su-generator-attr-container su-generator-skip" data-default=""><h5>Temps</h5><input type="text" name="time" value="" id="su-generator-attr-time" class="su-generator-attr" /><div class="su-generator-attr-desc">In this field you can specify one or more time ranges. Every day at this time the content of shortcode will be visible. <br><br> Examples (click to set) <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">9-18</b> - show content from 9:00 to 18:00 <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">9-13, 14-18</b> - show content from 9:00 to 13:00 and from 14:00 to 18:00 <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">9:30-10:15</b> - example with minutes (content will be visible each day, 45 minutes) <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">9:00:00-17:59:59</b> - example with seconds</div></div><div class="su-generator-attr-container su-generator-skip" data-default=""><h5>Days of the week</h5><input type="text" name="days_week" value="" id="su-generator-attr-days_week" class="su-generator-attr" /><div class="su-generator-attr-desc">In this field you can specify one or more days of the week. Every week at these days the content of shortcode will be visible. <br><br> 0 - Sunday <br> 1 - Monday <br> 2 - Tuesday <br> 3 - Wednesday <br> 4 - Thursday <br> 5 - Friday <br> 6 - Saturday <br><br> Examples (click to set) <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">1-5</b> - show content from Monday to Friday <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">0</b> - show content only at Sunday <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">0, 3-5</b> - show content at Sunday and from Wednesday to Friday</div></div><div class="su-generator-attr-container su-generator-skip" data-default=""><h5>Days of the month</h5><input type="text" name="days_month" value="" id="su-generator-attr-days_month" class="su-generator-attr" /><div class="su-generator-attr-desc">In this field you can specify one or more days of the month. Every month at these days the content of shortcode will be visible. <br><br> Examples (click to set) <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">1</b> - show content only at first day of month <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">1-5</b> - show content from 1th to 5th <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">10-15, 20-25</b> - show content from 10th to 15th and from 20th to 25th</div></div><div class="su-generator-attr-container su-generator-skip" data-default=""><h5>Months</h5><input type="text" name="months" value="" id="su-generator-attr-months" class="su-generator-attr" /><div class="su-generator-attr-desc">In this field you can specify the month or months in which the content will be visible. <br><br> Examples (click to set) <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">1</b> - show content only in January <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">2-6</b> - show content from February to June <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">1, 3, 5-7</b> - show content in January, March and from May to July</div></div><div class="su-generator-attr-container su-generator-skip" data-default=""><h5>Years</h5><input type="text" name="years" value="" id="su-generator-attr-years" class="su-generator-attr" /><div class="su-generator-attr-desc">In this field you can specify the year or years in which the content will be visible. <br><br> Examples (click to set) <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">2014</b> - show content only in 2014 <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">2014-2016</b> - show content from 2014 to 2016 <br><b class="su-generator-set-value" title="Cliquez sur pour définir cette valeur">2014, 2018, 2020-2022</b> - show content in 2014, 2018 and from 2020 to 2022</div></div><div class="su-generator-attr-container su-generator-skip" data-default=""><h5>Alternative text</h5><input type="text" name="alt" value="" id="su-generator-attr-alt" class="su-generator-attr" /><div class="su-generator-attr-desc">In this field you can type the text which will be shown if content is not visible at the current moment</div></div><div class="su-generator-attr-container"><h5>Contenu</h5><textarea name="su-generator-content" id="su-generator-content" rows="5">Scheduled content</textarea></div><div id="su-generator-preview"></div><div class="su-generator-actions su-generator-clearfix"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="button button-primary button-large su-generator-insert"><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Insérer le shortcode</a> <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="button button-large su-generator-toggle-preview"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i> Prévisualisation en direct</a> <div class="su-generator-presets alignright" data-shortcode="scheduler">\n	<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="button button-large su-gp-button"><i class="fa fa-bars"></i> Presets</a>\n	<div class="su-gp-popup">\n		<div class="su-gp-head">\n			<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="button button-small button-primary su-gp-new">Save current settings as preset</a>\n		</div>\n		<div class="su-gp-list">\n			<b>Presets not found</b>		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n		</div>', 'no'),
